biography:

Ellen is a senior data engineer at the engineering consultancy ThoughtWorks and one of the rare specimens of native Berliners. Her background includes data science, data engineering, and backend engineering. In her spare time, Ellen co-leads  „Data Science for Social Good Berlin“, an organization that brings together nonprofits and volunteer data scientists to work on social issues.
